    <h3>Community Support</h3>

    <p>In CADU we are involved with Mexico’s development and with the goal of eradicating extreme poverty.
      Therefore, we have continuously deployed several social programs, also since 2018 we have acquired a formal
      commitment to build a corporate social responsibility plan aligned to our business model.</p>

      <h3>Medical brigades</h3>

      <p>In 2018, through our Neighborhood Promoters program, we were able to create synergies with several governmental
        entities and civil associations to carry out medical brigades and provide health services in our developments. All
        these activities are promoted by CADU, not only due to our social commitment, also because we want our clients and
        communities to feel identified with the company. Among the services provided in 2018 were the following:</p>

        <ul class="c-content-list-1 c-theme c-separator-dot">
          <li>Free mammograms.</li>
          <li>General medical tests.</li>
          <li>Pediatrics consultation.</li>
          <li>Eye examinations.</li>
          <li>Prescription lenses giveaway with simbolic prices.</li>
          <li>Anti-rabies pet vaccination campaign .</li>
          <li>Inscriptions to elderly care programs and to the popular insurance scheme.</li>
        </ul>



